Audited Annual Accounts during the last Five (5) financial years i.e. upto 2020-21  for which the audited accounts are available to establish the capability of the bidder to successfully perform the tender and deliver the materials.

Minimum Average Annual Turnover (MAAT) :-  The vendor must have MAAT of at least INR Two  hundred Crores only  from the  cable, conductor & allied  business  for the best three (3) financial years out of last five (5) financial years ending March 2021.                                             ? For SSI unit of Bihar, vendor must have turnover of at least 50% of the MAAT requirement as mentioned above (i.e. INR 100 Crores only) from the  cable, conductor & allied  business  for any one year out of last five (5) financial years up to FY 2020-21.
Net Worth: - Net Worth of last three financial year upto FY 2020-21 shall be positive
